if you want to break that assumption to make a more interesting/elegant design, just mention it.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eI’m generally interested in more low-level stuff like scheduling, filesystems, messaging, syscall stuff, but if you have a burning desire to talk about using React on top of the NT kernel go for it.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThis shouldn’t need spelling out, but this is meant as a play space for ideas, so don’t be assholes to each other. If you disagree with a design decision, seek clarity and assume the person had a good reason for it. If somebody disagrees with \u003cem\u003eyou\u003c/em\u003e, assume they’re not trying to dunk on you.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo Lobsters, what’ve you got?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIf you’re not going to reply with concrete ideas or suggestions, or if you’re going to talk about how there’s no room for a new OS, or how the effort should be spent elsewhere…please keep it to yourself (or PMs). This is meant to be a thread for those with dreams, madness, hubris, and more than a little mischief in their hearts.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/jr4crd/what_should_new_os_have","submitter_user":{"username":"friendlysock","created_at":"2014-02-20T00:43:41.000-06:00","is_admin":false,"about":"*Literally* full of ants.\r\n\r\nFriendly engineer and human being.\r\n\r\nStrong opinions held weakly, sometimes weekly.\r\n\r\n\u003e Gentrification is the process by which nebulous threats are pacified and alchemised into money. \r\n","is_moderator":false,"karma":31574,"avatar_url":"/avatars/friendlysock-100.png","invited_by_user":"MasonJar"},"tags":["ask","osdev"]},{"short_id":"tyabnv","short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/tyabnv","created_at":"2020-11-24T22:59:29.000-06:00","title":"An API is a user interface","url":"https://www.arp242.net/api-ux.html","score":39,"flags":1,"comment_count":22,"description":"","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/